            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Delivery rate is the percentage of emails accepted by receiving servers (delivered minus bounced). Deliverability is the percentage that actually reach the inbox. An email can be delivered but still land in spam.</p></div></div>
          </div>
